\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 N\_a fost s\'e3 fie. Am auzit un salt \'een spatele meu, am sim\'feit mirosul \'een\'feep\'e3tor \'bai am scheunat. Omul\_tigru putea s\'e3 alerge la fel de repede ca mine.}{
\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \'ce}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n clipa aceea, mi\_am ad}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 us aminte de un ghid b\'e3tr\'e2n pe care\_l cunoscusem \'een Alaska \'bai mi\_am dorit mai mult dec\'e2t orice ca el s\'e3
 fi fost cu mine. Era un om\_urs kodiak. Apoi m\_am r\'e3sucit \'bai l\_am \'eent\'e2mpinat pe tigru, \'eenainte ca el s\'e3 m\'e3 atace.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Era o namil\'e3, de cel pu\'fein dou\'e3 sute cincizeci de kilograme. Ochii \'eei sc\'e2nteiau deasupra col\'feilor imen\'bai. Ridic\'e3 o lab\'e3 care}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{
