\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Afl\'e3 c\'e3 Suleiman cel \'cen\'feelept e mort de trei mii de ani, ripost\'e3 el. Mult, mult timp am l\'e2ncezit \'een celula mea str\'e2mt\'e3, eu care c\'e2ndva am f\'e3
