\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 O, tu, t\'e2rf\'e3 f\'e3r\'e3 v\'e3l \'bai neru\'bainat\'e3, cu p\'e3rul ca iadul, afl\'e3 c\'e3 eu sunt Rashid cel puternic, cel glorios \'een for\'fe\'e3, sf\'e3r\'e2m\'e3torul de st\'e2nci! Intr
