\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am a\'bateptat s\'e3 devin pe deplin con\'batient, \'eenainte de\_a accep\-ta o can\'e3 cu sup\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ce s\_a \'eent\'e2mplat cu mine? am \'baoptit; m\'e3 transformaser\'e3, fire\'bate, \'een om.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
