\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ei bine, la \'eentoarcere ar trebui s\_o lua\'fei pe\_a mea, continu\'e3 el. Altfel calea este primejdioas\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Avea dreptate. Un om normal s\_ar fi r\'e3t\'e3cit chiar pe lun\'e3 plin\'e3. C\'e3rarea era \'eengust\'e3, aproape \'batears\'e3, iar \'feinutul \emdash  acciden\-tat \'bai plin de umbre. Dac\'e3 \'ee\'fe
i pierdeai capul, puteai umbla pe coclauri p\'e2n\'e3\_n zori \'bai riscai s\'e3 te pr\'e3bu\'bae\'bati \'een gol \'bai s\'e3\_\'fei f}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 r\'e2ngi g\'e2tul.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Voi veni s\_o iau m\'e2ine sear\'e3, oft\'e3 bucuros Maledicto. Ah, domnule, c\'e2t sunte\'fei de bun! Oamenii proasp\'e3t c\'e3s\'e3tori\'fei sunt plini p\'e2n\'e3
 la refuz de dragoste, iar Cybelita este la fel de \'eensetat\'e3 de asta ca \'bai Amaris.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Sora dumitale? am \'eentrebat.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Da. A\'fei dori s\_o \'eent\'e2lni\'fei \'een seara asta?}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se l\'e3s\'e3 iar\'e3\'bai t\'e3cerea. Am cobor\'e2t \'eentr\_o r\'e2p\'e3 \'eentunecat\'e3, am ocolit un col\'fe de st\'e2nc\'e3 - \'bai n\_am mai putut s\'e3\_mi v\'e3d casa. Nimic altceva dec\'e2
t luciul stins al apei, str\'e3lucirea lunii \'een partea opus\'e3, stelele care pe nea\'bateptate deveniser\'e3 prea \'eendep\'e3rtate; doar acestea luminau \'feinutul. Am z\'e3rit zidurile n\'e3ruite al Fortalezei aproape deasupra capului nostru, \'ee
ncoron\'e2nd piscul ca din\-\'feii unei f\'e3lci. Maledicto \'bai cu mine am fi putut fi ultimele fiin\'fee v}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ii din Midgard.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cel\'e3lalt se opri. Lanterna din m\'e2na lui se stinse.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Noapte bun\'e3, se}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\langnp1048 \'f1}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 or Matuchek! strig\'e3 el.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 

\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 R\'e2sul \'eei r\'e3sun\'e3 malefic \'bai pl\'e3cut.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ce? Am clipit, buim\'e3cit, \'een p\'e2cla care m\'e3 \'eempresurase. Ce dracu' vrei s\'e3 spui? N\_am ajuns \'eenc\'e3 la castel!}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 . Mergi \'eentr\_acolo, dac\'e3 ai dorin\'fe\'e3. \'aai putin\'fe\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 I\_am auzit pa\'baii \'eentorc\'e2ndu\_se pe potec\'e3. Nu mai f\'e3ceau pietri\'baul s\'e3 scr\'e2\'baneasc\'e3. Erau u\'baori \'bai iu\'fei, ca ai unui animal s\'e3lt\'e3re\'fe.}{
\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \'ce}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 napoi spre vil\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Pentru moment, am r\'e3mas \'eencremenit. Auzeam o foarte sla\-b\'e3 suflare de v\'e2nt, fo\'banetul ierburilor uscate, cel al oceanului. Apoi b\'e3t\'e3ile inimii mele \'eenl\'e3turar\'e3 orice alt zgomot.}
{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\i\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ginny! }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 am urlat.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 M\_am \'eentors \'bai am alergat dup\'e3 el. M\_am \'eempiedicat de un bolovan, am c\'e3zut \'bai mi\_am julit m\'e2inile. M\_am ridicat cl\'e3tin\'e2ndu\_m\'e3, st\'e2ncile \'bai faleza mi\_au \'eentors 
\'eenjur\'e3turile \'bai am alunecat pe o pant\'e3, printre cactu\'bai \'bai tufi\'bauri. Iar\'e3\'bai m\_am \'eempiedicat de ceva \'bai am c\'e3zut. De data asta m\_am lovit cu capul de un bolo\-van. Impactul nu a fost serios, dar durerea m\_
a invadat, am v\'e3zut stele verzi \'bai pentru c\'e2teva clipe am z\'e3cut ame\'feit.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Iar \'een noapte am sim\'feit o prezen\'fe\'e3 nou\'e3. \'aai dincolo de sin\-gur\'e3tatea f\'e3r\'e3 speran\'fee ce se r\'e3sp\'e2ndea dintr\_\'eensa \'bai\_mi p\'e3trundea \'een inim\'e3 \'bai \'een m\'e3
duva oaselor, am sim\'feit o a\'bateptare \'eencordat\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ... }{\i\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 succ}{\i\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 es \'een capcana \'eentins\'e3 de mine la aceast\'e3 a treia \'eencercare... am\'e2ndoi \emdash 
 el mort \'bai ea corupt\'e3, dup\'e3 aceea zdrobi\-t\'e3 de remu\'bac\'e3ri... \'cen siguran\'fe\'e3 fa\'fe\'e3 de amenin\'fearea care vine dinspre ei ca o furtun\'e3, pe m\'e3sur\'e3 ce momentul acela se apro\-pie... \'cen sf\'e2r\'bait, \'een siguran
\'fe\'e3...}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai un g\'e2nd m\'e3 \'eenjunghie mult mai tare dec\'e2t orice durere: Maledicto nu putea s\_o z\'e3p\'e3ceasc\'e3 de unul singur, oricum nu at\'e2t de mult \'eenc\'e2t s\'e3 \'eenfr\'e2ng\'e3 dragostea, m
\'e2ndria \'bai decen\'fea ei... nu, Satana \'eensu\'bai lucrase asupra iubitei mele...}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu \'batiam ce inten\'feiona diavolul. Dar, ca un fulger, imaginea ei, singur\'e3 acolo cu Maledicto, m\'e3 eliber\'e3 de orice altceva, de durere, de sl\'e3biciune, sim\'feuri \'bai, pentru un timp, chiar 
\'bai de memoria Observatorului acela batjocoritor. Mi\_am urlat furia \'bai disperarea, am s\'e3rit \'een picioare \'bai am fugit.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Era nebunie curat\'e3. Nu\_mi d\'e3deam seama ce fac. F\'e3r\'e3 \'een\-doial\'e3 c\'e3 se inten\'feionase s\'e3 cad de pe o st\'e2nc\'e3 \'bai s\'e3\_mi rup g\'e2tul. Dar instinctele pe jum\'e3
tate animalice \'bai reflexele - b\'e3nuiesc - m\_au ferit de a\'baa ceva.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \'ce}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n cele di}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n urm\'e3 puterile m\_au l\'e3sat \'bai a trebuit s\'e3 m\'e3 opresc s\'e3\_mi trag sufletul. Acea pauz\'e3 for\'feat\'e3 i\_a oferit lucidit\'e3
\'feii mele o \'baans\'e3 de revenire.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Privind \'een jur, n\_am mai v\'e3zut nici castelul, nici vila. M\'e3 r\'e3t\'e3cisem.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
