\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se ghemui \'eentr\_un col\'fe \'een loc s\'e3 se apropie de mine. M\_am}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ridicat \'een picioare. Maledicto r\'e2nji, 
\'ee\'bai trecu o m\'e2n\'e3 pe dup\'e3 talia lui Ginny \'bai o trase spre el. Ea se cutremur\'e3, \'eencerc\'e2nd iar\'e3\'bai s\'e3\_l \'eendep\'e3rteze. O s\'e3rut\'e3, iar ea scoase un sunet nedeslu\'bait; \'eempotrivirea i se pref\'e3cu din nou \'ee
n gesturi dr\'e3g\'e3stoase. Am atacat. Maledicto m\'e3 lovi cu m\'e2na liber\'e3. Am c\'e3zut destul de ur\'e2t. Mi\_a pus un picior pe cap \'bai a ap\'e3sat.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu mi\_ar pl\'e3cea s\'e3\_\'fei f\'e3r\'e2m oasele, spuse, dar dac\'e3 nu ai gentile\'feea s\'e3 respec\'fei dorin\'feele unei doamne...}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\i\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dorin\'fee? }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ginny se smulse din str\'e2nsoare. Dumnezeule din Ceruri! se v\'e3it\'e3 ea. Ie\'bai afar\'e3!}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 

\par }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Maledicto chicoti.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ar trebui s\'e3 fug la auzul numelor sfinte, dac\'e3 vreo victim\'e3 de\_a mea le roste\'bate cu adev\'e3rat sincer, murmur\'e3 el. Dar tu voie\'bati s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2n aici. Cea mai mare dorin\'fe
\'e3 a ta este aceasta, Virginia.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ea \'een\'baf\'e3c\'e3 o vaz\'e3 \'bai o arunc\'e3 spre el. Demonul o prinse expert, din zbor, o sparse lovindu\_m\'e3 cu ea \'bai se duse la fereastr\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 O, da, d}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 e data aceasta vraja a fost rupt\'e3. Totu\'bai, nu ai team\'e3. M\'e3 voi \'eentoarce la un ceas mai prielnic.}{
\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Aerul undui vag, \'bai Maledicto disp\'e3ru peste pervaz. M\_am t\'e2r\'e2t dup\'e3 el. Terasa era alb\'e3 \'bai goal\'e3 \'een lumina lunii.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 M\_am a\'baezat, \'fein\'e2ndu\_mi capul \'een m\'e2ini. Ginny se l\'e3s\'e3 s\'e3 cad\'e3 l\'e2ng\'e3 mine, suspin\'e2nd. Trecu astfel mult timp. \'cen cele din urm\'e3 m\_am ridicat, am aprins lumina, am g
\'e3sit un trabuc \'bai m\_am a\'baezat pe marginea patului. Ea se ghemui l\'e2ng\'e3 genunchii mei, dar n\_am atins\_o.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ce\_a fost? am \'eentrebat\_o.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Un incubus.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
