\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Tunelul era lung \'bai \'eentortocheat \'bai se intersecta cu multe altele. Dac\'e3 nu a\'ba fi avut sim\'feul mirosului care s\'e3 m\'e3 ghideze, m\_a\'ba fi r\'e3t\'e3
cit foarte repede. Lumina venea de la m\'e2i\-nile a\'baezate deasupra chiliilor s\'e3pate \'een st\'e2nc\'e3 la intervale mari. Toat\'e3 lumea cuno\'batea faptul c\'e3 orice candidat la ini\'feiere petrecea aici, singur, o zi \'bai o noapte, iar evlavio
\'baii se \'eentorceau \'bai ei din c\'e2nd \'een c\'e2nd. Sufletul avea, pare\_se, de c\'e2\'batigat prin rug\'e3ciuni \'bai medita\'feii \'een singur\'e3tate. Dar nu \'batiam ce alte influen\'fee \'fei se infil\-trau atunci \'een subcon\'ba
tient. Anumite efluvii, aflate la limita per\-cep\'feiei mele de lup, \'eemi f\'e3ceau blana de pe g\'e2t s\'e3 se zb\'e2rleasc\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dup\'e3 un timp, acestea au fost total acoperite de mirosul \'een c\'e3utarea c\'e3ruia pornisem. Stomacul lupilor este mai rezistent dec\'e2t cel al oamenilor, totu\'bai de\_abia m\_am st\'e3p\'e2nit s\'e3
 nu vomit. C\'e2nd \'een cele din urm\'e3 am ajuns la surs\'e3, a trebuit s\'e3\_mi \'fein respira\'feia.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Str\'e3lucirea vag\'e3, alb\'e3struie, provenit\'e3 de la m\'e2na de dea\-supra intr\'e3rii lumina doar par\'feial chilia. Marmiadon dormea pe o saltea de paie. Purta rasa ca s\'e3\_i \'fein\'e3
 de cald; era la fel de soioas\'e3 ca \'bai pielea lui. \'cen rest, avea ni\'bate pesme\'fei, o gamel\'e3 cu ap\'e3, o can\'e3, o Biblie ioanin\'e3 \'bai o lum\'e2nare la lumina c\'e3reia s\'e3 citeasc\'e3. Probabil c\'e3\_\'bai p\'e3r\'e3
sea chilia doar ca s\'e3 mearg\'e3 la latrin\'e3. Nu c\'e3 ar fi fost mare diferen\'fe\'e3 dac\'e3 nu se ducea acolo. Pfuu!}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 M\_am dat \'eenapoi \'bai m\_am transformat \'een om. Efluviile nu m\'e3}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 mai afectau at\'e2t de tare, mai ales dup
\'e3 ce ra\'feiunea prelua contro\-lul. F\'e3r\'e3 \'eendoial\'e3 c\'e3 Marmiadon nici nu mai sim\'feea duhoarea.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am intrat \'een chilie, m\_am aplecat \'bai l\_am zg\'e2l\'fe\'e2it. Cu m\'e2na liber\'e3 am scos cu\'feitul.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ia s}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 coal\'e3\_te!}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Deschise ochii, m\'e3 v\'e3zu \'bai icni. Probabil c\'e3 eram o prezen\'fe\'e3 destul de amenin\'fe\'e3toare cum st\'e3team acolo, f\'e3r\'e3 pic de mil\'e3 pe chip \'bai \'eembr\'e3cat \'eentr\_
un costum sumar negru. In lumina aceea cadaveric\'e3, ar\'e3ta \'bai el destul de r\'e3u, av\'e2nd ochii \'eenfunda\'fei \'een orbite. I\_am acoperit gura cu m\'e2na \'eenainte s\'e3 poat\'e3 scoate vreun sunet Perii b\'e3rbii nerase \'eei erau ca ni\'ba
te \'feepi, carnea fe\'feei moale ca o coc\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dac\'e3 faci g\'e3l\'e3gie, i\_am spus aspru, \'ee\'fei v\'e3rs ma\'feele.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 F\'e3cu semn c\'e3 a \'een\'feeles \'bai l\_am eliberat.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 D\_d\_domnul }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Matuchek, \'baopti, retr\'e3g\'e2ndu\_se din calea mea p\'e2n\'e3 ajunse la perete.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am \'eencuviin\'feat.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Vreau s\'e3 vorbesc cu tine.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Eu... cum... Pentru numele lui Dumnezeu, despre ce?}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Despre cum s\'e3\_mi aduc \'eenapoi acas\'e3 fiica nev\'e3t\'e3mat\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Marmiadon f\'e3cu prin aer semnul crucii \'bai \'eenchipui \'bai alte simboluri.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 E\'bati posedat? Reu\'bai s\'e3 se uite la mine \'bai s\'e3\_\'bai r\'e3spund\'e3 singur la \'eentrebare: Nu. Pot s\'e3\_mi dau seama...}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu sunt nici subjugat de vreun demon, am morm\'e3it, \'bai nici psihopat. Vorbe\'bate!}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 D\_d\_dar n\_}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 am ce s\'e3\_\'fei spun. Fiica dumitale? Ce s\_a\_nt\'e2mplat? Nu \'batiam c\'e3 ai un copil.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 

\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Chestia asta m\'e3 dezorient\'e3. Nu min\'feea, n\_ar fi putut, \'een starea \'een care se afla.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cum a\'baa? am reu\'bait s\'e3 \'eengaim.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Se mai lini\'bati, \'ee\'bai c\'e3ut\'e3 ochelarii, \'bai\_i puse pe nas, dup\'e3 care m\'e3}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  privi iar.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 E purul adev\'e3r, insist\'e3. De ce\_a\'ba de\'feine informa\'feii despre familia dumitale? De ce\_ar avea nevoie de ele oricine de\_aici?}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Deoarece v\_a\'fei autodeclarat du\'bamanii mei, am spus furios.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Cl\'e3tin\'e3 din cap:}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Noi nu suntem du\'bamani ai omului. Cum am putea? Propov\'e3duim Evanghelia dragostei.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am m\'e2r\'e2it. \'ce\'bai cobor\'ee privirile.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ei bine, bolborosi, suntem \'bai noi fiii lui Adam. P\'e3c\'e3tuim \'bai noi, ca oricare al\'feii. Recunosc c\'e3 am fost furios c\'e2nd a\'fei f\'e3cut... scamatoria aceea... \'ce
mpotriva acelor nevinova\'fei...}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 A}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 m descris un arc cu cu\'feitul.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Las\'e3 balivernele, Marmiadon. Singurul nevinovat din toa\-t\'e3 chestia asta nenorocit\'e3 este o feti\'fe\'e3 de trei ani, care a fost dus\'e3 cu for\'fea \'een infern.}{
\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 R\'e3mase cu gura c\'e3scat\'e3. Ochii i se bulbucar\'e3.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Hai, scuip\'e3 tot ce \'batii, am sp}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 us.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Un timp, nu reu\'bai s\'e3 articuleze nici un cuv\'e2nt. Apoi, absolut \'eengrozit:}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu. Imposibil. Niciodat\'e3 n\_a\'ba... niciodat\'e3...}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Dar ceilal\'fei preo\'fei? Care dintre ei?}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nici unul. Jur. Nu se poate! - I\_am atins g\'e2tul cu v}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'e2rful cu\'feitului. Se cutremur\'e3. -}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048  Te rog}{
\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 , spune\_mi ce s\_a \'eent\'e2mplat. Vreau s\'e3 te ajut.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am l\'e3sat lama \'een jos, m\_am a\'baezat, mi\_am frecat g\'e2nditor b\'e3rbia \'bai m\_am \'eencruntat.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Uite ce e, l\_am \'eenvinuit, ai f\'e3cut tot ce se putea ca s\'e3\_mi tulburi traiul. \'aai acum, c\'e2nd via\'fea mea e distrus\'e3, ce pot s\'e3 cred? Dac\'e3 nu tu e\'bati r\'e3spunz\'e3
tor, ar trebui s\'e3 te str\'e3duie\'bati s\'e3 m\'e3 convingi de asta.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Ini\'feiatul \'eenghi\'fei \'een sec.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Eu... da, fire\'bate. N\_am vrut nimic r\'e3u. Numai ceea ce f\'e3cea\'fei voi - ceea ce face\'fei - este imoral. V\'e3 os\'e2ndi\'fei la chinurile iadului \'bai\_i ajuta\'fei \'bai pe ceilal\'fei s
\_o fac\'e3. Biserica nu poate s\'e3 r\'e3m\'e2n\'e3 nep\'e3s\'e3toare la a\'baa ceva. Foarte mul\'fei preo\'fei ai ei sunt gata s\'e3 se ofere voluntari pentru ca lucrul \'e3sta s\'e3 nu se \'eent\'e2mple.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Treci peste predic\'e3, i\_am poruncit.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu voiam s\'e3\_l las s\'e3 se ambaleze; altfel nu l\_a\'ba mai fi putut domina.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Rezum\'e3\_te la evenimente. Ai fost trimis s\'e3 instigi mul\'fei\-mea.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu. Nu s\'e3... Ei bine, eram pe lista voluntarilor. C\'e2nd s\_a oferit prilejul, mi s\_a \'eeng\'e3duit s\'e3 merg. Dar nu ca s\'e3... s\'e3 fac ce spui dumneata... ci s\'e3 dau ajutor}{
\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 , sfaturi, spriji}{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 n moral... \'bai, da, ei bine, da - s\'e3\_i ap\'e3r pe protestatari \'eempotriva eventualelor vr\'e3ji... Nimic altceva! Voi a\'fe
i fost cei care au atacat.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Sigur, sigur. Noi am \'eenceput prin a forma pichete \'bai, c\'e2nd chestia asta n\_a mers, am \'eenc\'e3lcat teritoriul fabricii, ne\_
am dedat la vandalisme, am instituit blocada, am terorizat... Oh\_oh. Iar tu ai ac\'feionat numai ca un simplu cet\'e3\'feean, astfel \'eenc\'e2t, atunci c\'e2nd ai dat gre\'ba, superiorii te\_au comp\'e3timit \'bai deja te\_au l\'e3sat s\'e3 te \'ee
ntorci la trebur}{\f1\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 ile cotidiene.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Isp\'e3\'baesc doar pentru p\'e3catul furiei, r\'e3spunse.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Am sim\'feit un fior pe \'baira spin\'e3rii. Ajunsesem la un moment important.}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
\par \emdash  }{\f227\fs24\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Nu te afli tu aici, jos, doar pentru c\'e3 te\_ai sup\'e3rat pe noi. Ce\_ai f\'e3cut de fapt?}{\f1\fs24\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
